{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"57123eb564","title":"关于要注意反革命复辟现象的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5c372a83ce","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"57123eb564"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"5c73b94eaa","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"57123eb564","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央文化革命小组办事组1967年2月25日编印的《快报》第一三三二号上。这期《快报》登载了题为《北京政法公社在天津小站公社支持了谁？》的材料。材料说：“1月26日，北京政法公社爆原长征队在天津小站公社坨子地大队，支持以四清运动中下台干部为背景的“爆原红色战斗队，抢走大队的大印，从此牛鬼蛇神纷纷出笼实行反攻倒算。”1967年2月27日，中共中央文化革命小组组长陈伯达把这期《快报》报送毛泽东时写道：“这是一个闹资本主义复辟的例子。革命群众要记者给主席反映情况。现在把材料送上，请顺便一阅。"}],"contents":[{"id":"fe2f90ce48","type":"title","text":"关于要注意反革命复辟现象的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"57123eb564"},{"id":"5c73b94eaa","type":"paragraph","text":"从上至下各级都有这种反革命复辟的现象，值得注意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"57123eb564"},{"id":"9756a336bd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"57123eb564"},{"id":"e11fa1ab1c","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"57123eb564"}],"page":{"id":"300fabd1b1","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"57123eb564","start":346,"end":346}}}},"__N_SSG":true}